➜网飞《龙之信条》动画预告公开 随从少女名曰汉娜
http://www.sohu.com/a/414765510_392483	9430
<p>Netflix此前公开了与卡普空联动推出《龙之信条》同名游戏改编动画剧集，并定档9月17日。随着距离上映还有不到一个月时间，官方正式公开了本作的预告片段。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=211517749&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200825/18299cb6288c4b69bc3af9d739027b14.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200825/b0804fdc0e664d09988da6f2b0202303.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200825/287a9c06573549d0a49221729e518170.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
